  <name>Butter Visualizer</name>
  <summary>Multi-window audio-reactive visualization application</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Butter Visualizer is a powerful audio visualization application powered by Butterchurn.
      Create unlimited popup windows with independent visualizations, capture live microphone
      audio, and stream to multiple displays with low-latency WebRTC audio streaming.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-window visualizations with independent Butterchurn presets</li>
      <li>Live microphone audio capture</li>
      <li>WebRTC audio-only streaming to visualization windows</li>
      <li>200+ Butterchurn presets with visual thumbnails</li>
      <li>Dark mode UI</li>
      <li>Remote control via REST API and Socket.IO</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

